                    "body": "Actually, there is a helper for decimal operations in the [Gandiva C++ base|https://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/master/cpp/src/gandiva/decimal_type_util.h] and in the [Java implementation|https://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/master/java/gandiva/src/main/java/org/apache/arrow/gandiva/evaluator/DecimalTypeUtil.java].\r\n\r\nI'm thinking I will close this issue and instead:\r\n\r\n# Add exposing the Decimal utility to the Python implementation to ARROW-13918\r\n# Add documentation of this utility to ARROW-10154",
